						<?php if ( get_theme_mod( 'si_logo' ) ) : ?>
							<img src="<?php echo esc_url( get_theme_mod( 'si_logo', si_doc_header_logo_url() ) ); ?>" alt="document logo" >
						<?php else : ?>
							<img src="<?php echo esc_url( si_doc_header_logo_url() ) ?>" alt="document logo" >
						<?php endif; ?>
					</div><!-- #logo -->
					

					<div id="title">

						<div class="current_status">
							<?php if ( 'write-off' === si_get_invoice_status() ) : ?>
								<span><?php esc_html_e( 'Void', 'sprout-invoices' ) ?></span>
							<?php elseif ( ! si_get_invoice_balance() ) : ?>
								<span><?php esc_html_e( 'Paid', 'sprout-invoices' ) ?></span>
							<?php elseif ( 'temp' === si_get_invoice_status() ) : ?>
								<span><?php esc_html_e( 'Not Yet Published', 'sprout-invoices' ) ?></span>
							<?php else : ?>
								<span><?php esc_html_e( 'Payment Pending', 'sprout-invoices' ) ?></span>
							<?php endif; ?>
						</div>


						<h1><?php the_title() ?></h1>
	
					</div><!-- #title -->

				</div>
			</div>
		</header>

		<section class="row" id="intro">
			<div class="inner">
				<div class="column">
					
					<h2><?php _e( 'From', 'sprout-invoices' ) ?></h2>

					<h3><?php si_company_name() ?></h3>
					
					<?php si_doc_address() ?>

					<?php if ( si_get_company_phone() ) : ?>
						<div class="company_info"><?php printf( __( 'Phone: %1$s', 'sprout-invoices' ), si_get_company_phone() ) ?></div>
					<?php endif ?>

					<?php if ( si_get_company_fax() ) : ?>
						<div class="company_info"><?php printf( __( 'Phone: %1$s', 'sprout-invoices' ), si_get_company_fax() ) ?></div>
					<?php endif ?>

					<?php if ( si_get_company_email() ) : ?>
						<div class="company_info"><?php printf( __( '%1$s', 'sprout-invoices' ), si_get_company_email() ) ?></div>
					<?php endif ?>

					<?php if ( si_get_invoice_client_id() ) :  ?>
						
						<h2 class="client_to"><?php _e( 'To', 'sprout-invoices' ) ?></h2>
						
						<div id="client_info">
							
							<h3><?php echo get_the_title( si_get_invoice_client_id() ) ?></h3>
						 
							<?php si_client_address( si_get_invoice_client_id() ) ?>

							<?php if ( si_get_client_phone() ) : ?>
								<div class="company_info"><?php printf( __( 'Phone: %1$s', 'sprout-invoices' ), si_get_client_phone() ) ?></div>
							<?php endif ?>

							<?php if ( si_get_client_fax() ) : ?>
								<div class="company_info"><?php printf( __( 'Fax: %1$s', 'sprout-invoices' ), si_get_client_fax() ) ?></div>
							<?php endif ?>

							<?php do_action( 'si_document_client_addy' ) ?>
							

						</div><!-- #client_info -->

					<?php endif ?>

					<?php do_action( 'si_document_vcards' ) ?>

				</div>

				<div class="column">

					<div class="invoice_info"><?php printf( '<span class="info">%1$s</span> %2$s', __( 'Invoice #', 'sprout-invoices' ), si_get_invoice_id() ) ?></div>

					<?php if ( si_get_invoice_po_number() ) : ?>
						<div class="invoice_info"><?php printf( '<span class="info">%1$s</span> %2$s', __( 'PO #', 'sprout-invoices' ), si_get_invoice_po_number() ) ?></div>
